name: Galaxy Rocket Boost
description:
Greetings Future Space Explorer!

In Galaxy Rocket Boost, you are a spaceship on a mission to make a fast escape from the boundaries of gravity.

Collect special money stars to unlock new, fancy rockets.

With simple quick tap controls, your number one objective is to go up, up, and away.

Maneuver with rapid and frustrating precision around puzzling obstacles tailor made and designed to make you fail.

How high can YOU go? Aim for the top with leaderboards to compete against other cadets.
